<item>
    <title>【Financial RAG Demo 项目】知识库构建</title>
    <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/project-research/financial-rag-demo/260217-financial-rag-demo-knowledge-base-construction/</link>
    <pubDate>Tue, 17 Feb 2026 22:12:35 &#43;0800</pubDate>
    <author>Author</author>
    <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/project-research/financial-rag-demo/260217-financial-rag-demo-knowledge-base-construction/</guid>
    <description><![CDATA[<h2 id="-初始化-__init__self">🚀 初始化 <code>__init__(self)</code></h2>
<h3 id="1-初始化向量数据库">1. 初始化向量数据库</h3>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-python" data-lang="python"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">chroma</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Chroma</span><span class="p">(</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">	    <span class="n">collection_name</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&#34;rag&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">	    <span class="n">embedding_function</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">DashScopeEmbeddings</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">model</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&#34;text-embedding-v4&#34;</span><span class="p">),</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">	    <span class="n">persist_directory</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&#34;./chromadb&#34;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="p">)</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><ul>
<li>使用<code>langchain_chroma</code>的<code>Chroma</code>。</li>
<li>定义三个参数：
<ul>
<li><code>collection_name</code>：数据库的名称。</li>
<li><code>embedding_function</code>：向量转换使用的模型。</li>
<li><code>persist_directory</code>：数据库的位置，持久化地址。</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>模型使用<code>langchain_community.embeddings</code>的<code>DashScopeEmbeddings</code>，阿里云通义千问的类。</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="2-初始化文本分割器">2. 初始化文本分割器</h3>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-python" data-lang="python"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">spliter</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter</span><span class="p">(</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="n">chunk_size</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">300</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="n">chunk_overlap</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">30</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="n">separators</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">&#34;</span><span class="se">\n\n</span><span class="s2">&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s2">&#34;</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="s2">&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s2">&#34;.&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s2">&#34;!&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s2">&#34;?&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s2">&#34;。&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s2">&#34;！&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s2">&#34;？&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s2">&#34; &#34;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s2">&#34;&#34;</span><span class="p">],</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="n">length_function</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nb">len</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="p">)</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><ul>
<li>使用<code>langchain_text_splitters</code>的<code>RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter</code>。</li>
<li>定义四个参数：
<ul>
<li><code>chunk_size</code>：文本块最大长度，计算方法用<code>length_function</code>指定。</li>
<li><code>chunk_overlap</code>：相邻文本块重叠的字符数。</li>
<li><code>separators</code>：分割时检测的分隔符，一个列表，按顺序决定优先级。先尝试用<code>&quot;\n\n&quot;</code> (段落) 分割，若超过最大长度再尝试<code>&quot;\n&quot;</code>。</li>
<li><code>length_function</code>：指定长度计算方法。<code>len</code>表示用 Python 的<strong>字符</strong>计算，任何一个文本单位都算一个字符。</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="-主函数-upload_by_strself-data-str-filename">🛠️ 主函数 <code>upload_by_str(self, data: str, filename)</code></h2>
<h3 id="1-md5-去重">1. MD5 去重</h3>
<ol>
<li>流程：计算文件的 MD5  -&gt; 检测是否已有相同 MD5 -&gt; 保存未处理过的 MD5</li>
<li><strong>哈希对象 (HASH)</strong>
<ol>
<li>意义：接收<strong>字节序列</strong>，内部处理后返回 32 位的字符串。</li>
<li>一般流程：
<ol>
<li>使用字符串的<code>encode()</code>方法把文件转换为<strong>字节序列</strong>；</li>
<li>调用<code>hashlib</code>模块的哈希算法函数，如<code>md5()</code>、<code>sha1()</code>、<code>sha256()</code>、<code>blake2b</code>生成对应的哈希对象；</li>
<li>使用<code>update()</code>方法传入字节序列；</li>
<li>使用<code>digest()</code>或<code>hexdigest()</code>(分别是二进制和十六进制) 完成计算并取出字符串。</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li>对比阶段实际生产可用 SQLite 来存储。</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="2-分割器">2. 分割器</h3>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-python" data-lang="python"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">knowledge_chunks</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">self</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">spliter</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">split_text</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>使用<code>spliter</code>的<code>split_text()</code>方法，接收字符串，返回一个<strong>列表</strong>，里面是切好的字符串。</p>]]></description>
</item>
<item>
    <title>【Financial RAG Demo 项目】概览</title>
    <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/project-research/financial-rag-demo/260211-financial-rag-demo-outline/</link>
    <pubDate>Wed, 11 Feb 2026 21:54:52 &#43;0800</pubDate>
    <author>Author</author>
    <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/project-research/financial-rag-demo/260211-financial-rag-demo-outline/</guid>
    <description><![CDATA[<h2 id="-项目定位">🎯 项目定位</h2>
<h3 id="1-项目名称">1. 项目名称</h3>
<p>基于 RAG 技术的金融领域智能客服系统</p>
<h3 id="2-技术栈">2. 技术栈</h3>
<p>Python + LangChain + 通义千问 + Chroma + Streamlit</p>
<h3 id="3-核心功能">3. 核心功能</h3>
<ul>
<li>知识库管理</li>
<li>检索增强式对话</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="-技术架构">🏗️ 技术架构</h2>
<p>整个项目分为两个线索，分别是<strong>把文件嵌入向量数据库</strong>、<strong>根据用户提问检索数据库并返回结果</strong>。</p>]]></description>
</item>
<item>
    <title>【效率备忘】Microsoft VS Code 配置推荐</title>
    <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/efficiency-memos/250413-vscode-deploy/</link>
    <pubDate>Sun, 13 Apr 2025 22:21:54 &#43;0800</pubDate>
    <author>Author</author>
    <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/efficiency-memos/250413-vscode-deploy/</guid>
    <description><![CDATA[<h2 id="-全局设置">🛠️ 全局设置</h2>
<h3 id="1-程序设置">1. 程序设置</h3>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-json" data-lang="json"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 程序设置
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"></span><span class="s2">&#34;update.enableWindowsBackgroundUpdates&#34;</span><span class="err">:</span> <span class="kc">false</span><span class="err">,</span>	<span class="c1">// 禁止后台下载更新
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"></span><span class="s2">&#34;update.mode&#34;</span><span class="err">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;none&#34;</span><span class="err">,</span>							<span class="c1">// 禁止任何更新行为
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"></span><span class="s2">&#34;extensions.autoCheckUpdates&#34;</span><span class="err">:</span> <span class="kc">false</span><span class="err">,</span>           <span class="c1">// 禁止插件检查更新
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"></span><span class="s2">&#34;extensions.autoUpdate&#34;</span><span class="err">:</span> <span class="kc">false</span><span class="err">,</span>                 <span class="c1">// 禁止插件自动更新
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"></span><span class="s2">&#34;extensions.ignoreRecommendations&#34;</span><span class="err">:</span> <span class="kc">true</span><span class="err">,</span>		<span class="c1">// 关闭插件安装建议
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"></span><span class="s2">&#34;files.autoGuessEncoding&#34;</span><span class="err">:</span> <span class="kc">true</span><span class="err">,</span>				<span class="c1">// 打开文件时猜测字符集编码
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"></span><span class="s2">&#34;explorer.compactFolders&#34;</span><span class="err">:</span> <span class="kc">false</span><span class="err">,</span>				<span class="c1">// 关闭文件夹紧凑显示模式
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"></span><span class="s2">&#34;chat.agentsControl.enabled&#34;</span><span class="err">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;hidden&#34;</span><span class="err">,</span>			<span class="c1">// 关闭 Copilot 代理控制功能
</span></span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id="2-工作区设置">2. 工作区设置</h3>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-json" data-lang="json"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 工作区设置
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"></span><span class="s2">&#34;workbench.startupEditor&#34;</span><span class="err">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;none&#34;</span><span class="err">,</span>				<span class="c1">// 关闭启动页面
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"></span><span class="s2">&#34;workbench.editor.empty.hint&#34;</span><span class="err">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;hidden&#34;</span><span class="err">,</span>		<span class="c1">// 编辑器为空时，不提示打开文件
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"></span><span class="s2">&#34;workbench.list.smoothScrolling&#34;</span><span class="err">:</span> <span class="kc">true</span><span class="err">,</span>			<span class="c1">// 开启界面平滑滚动效果
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"></span><span class="s2">&#34;workbench.colorTheme&#34;</span><span class="err">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;Dracula Theme Soft&#34;</span><span class="err">,</span>	<span class="c1">// 用 Dracula Theme Official 插件设置主题外观
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"></span><span class="s2">&#34;workbench.iconTheme&#34;</span><span class="err">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;material-icon-theme&#34;</span><span class="err">,</span>	<span class="c1">// 用 Material Icon Theme 插件设置图标样式
</span></span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id="3-编辑器设置">3. 编辑器设置</h3>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-json" data-lang="json"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 编辑器设置
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"></span><span class="s2">&#34;editor.fontSize&#34;</span><span class="err">:</span> <span class="mi">18</span><span class="err">,</span>							<span class="c1">// 字体大小
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"></span><span class="s2">&#34;editor.mouseWheelZoom&#34;</span><span class="err">:</span> <span class="kc">true</span><span class="err">,</span>					<span class="c1">// 允许使用 ctrl + 滚轮缩放字体大小
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"></span><span class="s2">&#34;editor.fontFamily&#34;</span><span class="err">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;Consolas, &#39;微软雅黑&#39;&#34;</span><span class="err">,</span>	 <span class="c1">// 设置字体
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"></span><span class="s2">&#34;editor.smoothScrolling&#34;</span><span class="err">:</span> <span class="kc">true</span><span class="err">,</span>					<span class="c1">// 开启编辑器区域平滑滚动效果
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"></span><span class="s2">&#34;editor.cursorSmoothCaretAnimation&#34;</span><span class="err">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;on&#34;</span><span class="err">,</span>		<span class="c1">// 开启光标平滑移动效果
